---
// Section Horaires et tarifs
---

<section
  id="horaires-tarifs"
  class="mb-16 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 md:p-10 border border-gray-100"
  aria-labelledby="horaires-tarifs-heading"
>
  <h2
    id="horaires-tarifs-heading"
    class="mb-6 text-2xl md:text-3xl text-center"
  >
    <a href="/tarifs/" class="no-underline text-inherit hover:text-accent transition-colors">
      Horaires et tarifs
    </a>
  </h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <article
      class="bg-secondary/35 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100"
      aria-labelledby="tarifs-heading"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-full mr-4">
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-600"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 id="tarifs-heading" class="text-xl font-bold text-tertiary">
          Tarifs des consultations
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
              <th
                scope="col"
                class="py-3 pr-4 text-sm font-semibold text-tertiary"
                >Prestation</th
              >
              <th
                scope="col"
                class="py-3 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-tertiary whitespace-nowrap"
                >Temps</th
              >
              <th
                scope="col"
                class="py-3 pl-4 text-sm font-semibold text-tertiary text-right"
                >Tarif</th
              >
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700"
                >Consultation individuelle</td
              >
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap"
                >45 min</td
              >
              <td
                class="py-3 pl-4 text-right text-xl font-bold text-tertiary"
                >80€</td
              >
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700"
                >Consultation MOSAIC</td
              >
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap"
                >1h</td
              >
              <td
                class="py-3 pl-4 text-right text-xl font-bold text-tertiary"
                >90€</td
              >
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700"
                >Consultation de couple</td
              >
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap"
                >1h</td
              >
              <td
                class="py-3 pl-4 text-right text-xl font-bold text-tertiary"
                >110€</td
              >
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-gray-700">Mon Soutien Psy*</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap"
                >30 min</td
              >
              <td
                class="py-3 pl-4 text-right text-xl font-bold text-tertiary"
                >50€</td
              >
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mt-4 p-3 bg-secondary/60 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg"
      >
        <p class="text-sm text-tertiary">
          <strong>*Mon Soutien Psy :</strong> Ces séances remboursées ne peuvent
          être prises qu'avec mon accord préalable. <a
            href="/mon-soutien-psy/"
            class="text-link underline hover:no-underline"
          >
            Voir les conditions d'accès
          </a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mt-3 p-3 bg-secondary/60 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg"
      >
        <p class="text-sm text-tertiary">
          <strong>💳 Paiement :</strong> Chèques, espèces et virement bancaire.
          Cartes bancaires non acceptées.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article
      class="bg-secondary/35 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100"
      aria-labelledby="horaires-heading"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-full mr-4">
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-600"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3
          id="horaires-heading"
          class="text-xl font-bold text-tertiary"
        >
          Horaires d'ouverture
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div
          class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-100"
        >
          <span class="text-gray-700">Lundi, mardi et vendredi</span>
          <span class="font-semibold text-tertiary">8h00 - 20h00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Autres jours</span>
          <span class="text-red-700 font-semibold">Fermé</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="mt-4 p-3 bg-secondary/60 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg"
      >
        <p class="text-sm text-tertiary">
          <strong>📅 Prise de rendez-vous :</strong> Consultations sur rendez-vous
          uniquement. <a href="/consulter/" class="text-link underline hover:no-underline">Voir les modalités de consultation</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <a
          href="/consulter/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-primary/30 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-tertiary no-underline transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-secondary/40"
        >
          En savoir plus avant de consulter
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.doctolib.fr/psychologue/sceaux/nicolas-devaux-sceaux/booking?utm_campaign=website-button&utm_source=nicolas-devaux-sceaux-website-button&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=withpreview-white-inlined&utm_term=nicolas-devaux-sceaux"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[#0B5F8A] px-4 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white no-underline transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#094A6E]"
          data-track-doctolib
          data-track-location="Horaires Tarifs"
        >
          Prendre rendez-vous
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
